**Sidebar**: 
- Tabs? The sidebar is getting big. Add sections: keep sites list, add region filter chips (dropdown select maybe — chips per region could overflow; a `<select>` "All regions" is compact). Add a "Pins" section? Pins are managed on the map mostly. Let me add:
  - Region filter: select dropdown (All regions / each region / Unassigned).
  - Add buttons row: "Add site" and "Add region" and pin mode. Three buttons is a lot; I can do a segmented row: [＋ Site] [＋ Pin] [＋ Region]. 
