Seed data: add 3 regions (circles covering the seed sites areas), a couple of pins, maybe one report and status history entries for seeds, and named assignments for seeds. Photos can't be seeded (no images) — fine.

volunteersJoined removal → migration. Seed assignments: generate names list.

